    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically sound E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54B32 3.2L inline-six engine with individual throttle bodies and double-VANOS. This driver-focused example utilizes a Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox and a limited-slip rear differential for precise power delivery. The suspension geometry remains true, benefiting from recent bushing refreshes and proactive rear subframe reinforcement. While showing minor cosmetic patina consistent with a well-loved performance vehicle, its mechanical health is robust, having undergone recent valve clearance adjustments and cooling system overhauls. A turn-key enthusiast machine ready for the twisties.",
